tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE customer_feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  rating INT,
  feedback_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE feedback (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    feedback TEXT,
    rating INT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE customers (
    customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    phone_number TEXT,
    address TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE services (
    service_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    service_name TEXT,
    description TEXT,
    category TEXT,
    provider_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE providers (
    provider_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    provider_name TEXT,
    services_offered TEXT,
    location TEXT,
    contact_number TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE ratings (
    rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    service_id INT,
    customer_id INT,
    rating_value INT,
    feedback TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);
